# Regulatory Disclosures Transaction Residual Maturity Number

## identifier
de15192

## type
int

## definition
This is the number of days of residual maturity, which is the remaining term to contractual maturity.

## guidance
Please enter a whole number greater than or equal to zero to the nearest day for a transaction with a defined term or as "-1" for an undefined (open) transaction.
Where the transaction collateral types are long-term asset-backed securities or equity securities, report the residual maturity of the collateral as "-1".

## syntax
### xbrl
- name=RegulatoryDisclosures.TransactionResidualMaturity.Number
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.35
- period=instant
